cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on image manipulation tasks using GANs, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also introduces a novel adversarial contrasting objective, which is related to adversarial training and optimization (cs.AI). The manipulation tasks involve changing the semantic meaning of objects, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
